标准\n    33\t> 以上验收标准的完整 Gherkin 用例详见 `tests/bdd/im.feature`。\n  
 34\t\n    35\t```gherkin\n    36\tFeature: Start Chatting After Match\n    37\t
 Scenario: Matched users see system welcome message\n    38\t    Given Alice and
